n \to \infty
\lim_{n\to\infty}\sum_{k=1}^n \sin{\left ( \frac{n}{n^2+k^2}\right )} = \lim_{n\to\infty}\frac1{n}\sum_{k=1}^n \frac1{1+\frac{k^2}{n^2}}
\int_0^1 \frac{dx}{1+x^2} = \frac{\pi}{4} 
